{"id":205,"parent_id":202,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":205,"title":"2 Thessalonians 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Thes.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","Pray for the triumph of the gospel cause—Paul preaches the gospel of work—Be not weary in well-doing."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.1","order":"03.16.003.21935"},["b","1"],"Finally, brethren, pray for us, that the word of the Lord",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"may have",["i","free"],"course"],", and be glorified, even as",["i","it is"],"with you:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.2","order":"03.16.003.21936"},["b","2"],"And that we may be delivered from",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"unreasonable"],"and wicked men: for all",["i","men"],"have not faith."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.3","order":"03.16.003.21937"},["b","3"],"But the Lord is faithful, who shall stablish you, and keep",["i","you"],"from",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"evil"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.4","order":"03.16.003.21938"},["b","4"],"And we have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"confidence"],"in the Lord touching you, that ye both do and will do the things which we command you."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.5","order":"03.16.003.21939"},["b","5"],"And the Lord",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"direct"],"your hearts into the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"love"],"of God, and into the patient waiting for Christ."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.6","order":"03.16.003.21940"},["b","6"],"Now we command you, brethren, in the name of our Lord Jesus Christ, that ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"withdraw"],"yourselves from every brother that walketh",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"disorderly"],", and not after the tradition which he received of us."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.7","order":"03.16.003.21941"},["b","7"],"For yourselves know how ye ought to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"follow"],"us: for we",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"behaved"],"not ourselves disorderly among you;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.8","order":"03.16.003.21942"},["b","8"],"Neither did we eat any man’s bread",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"for nought"],"; but wrought with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"labour"],"and travail night and day, that we might not be chargeable to any of you:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.9","order":"03.16.003.21943"},["b","9"],"Not because we have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"power"],", but to make ourselves an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"ensample"],"unto you to follow us."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.10","order":"03.16.003.21944"},["b","10"],"For even when we were with you, this we commanded you, that if any would not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"work"],", neither should he eat."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.11","order":"03.16.003.21945"},["b","11"],"For we hear that there are some which walk among you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"disorderly"],", working not at all, but are busybodies."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.12","order":"03.16.003.21946"},["b","12"],"Now them that are such we command and exhort by our Lord Jesus Christ, that with quietness they work, and eat their own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"bread"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.13","order":"03.16.003.21947"},["b","13"],"But ye, brethren, be not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"weary"],"in well doing."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.14","order":"03.16.003.21948"},["b","14"],"And if any man obey not our word by this epistle, note that man, and have no company with him, that he may be ashamed."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.15","order":"03.16.003.21949"},["b","15"],"Yet count",["i","him"],"not as an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"enemy"],", but",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"admonish"],["i","him"],"as a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"brother"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.16","order":"03.16.003.21950"},["b","16"],"Now the Lord of peace himself give you peace always by all means. The Lord",["i","be"],"with you all."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.17","order":"03.16.003.21951"},["b","17"],"The salutation of Paul with mine own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"hand"],", which is the token in every epistle: so I write."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.18","order":"03.16.003.21952"},["b","18"],"The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ",["i","be"],"with you all. Amen."]],["div",{"order":".000.21997"},[".closing","¶ The second",["i","epistle"],"to the Thessalonians was written from Athens.",["a",{"href":"fn_1"},"*"]]],[".studyNotes"]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.1a","order":"03.16.003.21953"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"may progress freely, rapidly."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.2a","order":"03.16.003.21955"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"unsuitable, absurd, improper."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.3a","order":"03.16.003.21957"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"the evil one, the devil."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.4a","order":"03.16.003.21959"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dependability"},"TG  Dependability"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.5a","order":"03.16.003.21961"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guidance-divine"},"TG  Guidance, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.5b","order":"03.16.003.21963"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/11.13"},"Deut. 11:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.6a","order":"03.16.003.21965"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/5.9.1-13"},"1 Cor. 5:9 (1–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/1.24.21-24"},"Alma 1:24 (21–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.57.56-57"},"5:57 (56–57)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/excommunication"},"TG  Excommunication"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.6b","order":"03.16.003.21967"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/16.17.17-19"},"Rom. 16:17 (17–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.7a","order":"03.16.003.21969"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"imitate."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.7b","order":"03.16.003.21971"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.5"},"1 Thes. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.8a","order":"03.16.003.21973"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],"undeservedly, gratuitously."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.8b","order":"03.16.003.21975"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/work-value-of"},"TG  Work, Value of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.9a","order":"03.16.003.21977"},["b","9a"],["span.small","GR"],"authority."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.9b","order":"03.16.003.21979"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/example"},"TG  Example"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.10a","order":"03.16.003.21981"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idleness"},"TG  Idleness"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/industry"},"Industry"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/labor"},"Labor"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/laziness"},"Laziness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.11a","order":"03.16.003.21983"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/5.14"},"1 Thes. 5:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.12a","order":"03.16.003.21985"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bread"},"TG  Bread"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.13a","order":"03.16.003.21987"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.9"},"Gal. 6:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.15a","order":"03.16.003.21989"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/enemies"},"TG  Enemies"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.15b","order":"03.16.003.21991"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/warn"},"TG  Warn"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.15c","order":"03.16.003.21993"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"},"TG  Brotherhood and Sisterhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.17a","order":"03.16.003.21995"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.18"},"Col. 4:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"fn1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.fn1","order":".000.21998"},["b","*"],"More recent scholarship concludes that 1 and 2 Thes. were most likely written from Corinth."]]}
